superMiscConds.notes: The Defendant is to abide by all rules and conditions of the Agent.  The Defendant is to maintain absolute sobriety - no alcohol or drugs unless prescribed by a physician.  The Defendant is to have no contact with minors unless approved by Agent.  The Defendant is to provide a biological specimen for DNA analysis, unless already provided.  The Defendant is to undergo a sex offender assessment and comply with any recommended treatment.  The Defendant is to comply with sex offender registry.  The Defendant is not to use the internet or possess any electronic device capable for internet without Agent approval (needs Agent's approval for work-related business).
